Enums to depict the properties that can be passed to a sycl::queue constructor.
DPCTL device has an associated set of aspects which identify characteristics of the device.
Redefinition of DPC++-specific Sycl backend types.
DPCTL device types that are equivalent to Sycl's device_type.

detaileddescription.para: This header defines dpctl specific enum types that wrap corresponding Sycl enum classes. These enums are defined primarily so that Python extensions that use DPCTL do not have to include Sycl headers directly.
